tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE tax_deductions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    client_id INT REFERENCES clients(id),
    deduction_type VARCHAR(50),
    amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    deduction_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    client_id INT,
    employee_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    total_deductions DECIMAL(10, 2)
);
